Circon rejects U . S . Surgical bid . Circon Corp said its board rejected U . S . Surgical Corp ' s revised $ 17 per share bid for all its outstanding shares . The bid had been revised down from a previous offer of $ 18 per share . " We are surprised at U . S . Surgical ' s latest maneuver , " Richard Auhil , Circon chairman said in a statement . " Circon ' s third quarter performance was an improvement over the second quarter and the year is shaping up the way we expected . The $ 18 per share offer was inadequate . This latest proposal , like its predecessor , is entirely inadequate . " 
